{"tid":1002530,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"危險的兔子墊材! 注意!","createTime":"2019-01-31T04:21:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T07:39:59.000Z","uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"650f9c1b8fcbdcd5aac1e6dfb980b3a42fb68712","tid":1002530,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"不要買松木及紅杉木的木屑(Pine shavings &amp; Cedar Shavings)，因為有種化學物質叫酚(Aromatic Phenols)會傷兔子的肝和呼吸系統。Pine pellets或其他墊材就沒問題，<span style=\"color: red;\">買的時候最好看清楚英文名字 !</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   因為依然有很多寵物店售賣這類型的墊材。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>總括來說，以下的墊材是對兔子<em><ins>有害</ins></em>：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Pine shavings and cedar shavings<br />\n2. Clay/Clumping litter<br />\n3. Corn cob litter<br />\n4. Scented litter<br />\n5. Newspaper / Shredded paper<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以下是對兔子<em><ins>安全</ins></em>的：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Paper pulp, 即是Carefresh (但貴！)<br />\n2. Compressed newspaper<br />\n3. Compressed sawdust pellets, 即是 Feline Pine, Wood stove pellets, Horse stall pellets (吸收力強，所以推介!)<br />\n<br />\n資訊來源: <a href=\"https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fcare%2Fshavings.html&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=0e0aee4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/care/shavings.html</a><br />\n                 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/JKevuEvgfyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJKevuEvgfyM&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=e3d92080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JKevuEvgfyM</a>"},{"pid":"4f935eb97e3ff4c55422911c0d16438f3477123b","tid":1002530,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T04:03:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子奮身救貓貓！😺🐰</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n當兔子側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西。兔子也有遠視。兔子正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。牠們只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/y-0xUyL8V5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fy-0xUyL8V5s&d=h41GIreLF%2BIJLuW8J2uc6pbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=07feb37a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/y-0xUyL8V5s</a>"},{"pid":"2d7a17ec1ee85ce074fe3d06db2730316454e409","tid":1002530,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:39:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}